<p data-index="913"><sup data-index="914"><a id="c17-tnote-0009" href="#c17-tnote-0009-1" data-index="915" data-section-index="27" data-section-idref="c17-tnote-0009-1" data-target-data-index="796">d</a></sup>$107,435 = $108,111 − $676</p></td>
