<p data-index="948"></p>
<p data-index="949"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="17-7" id="Page_17-7" data-index="950"></span>At December 31, 2019, Graff makes the following entry to recognize interest revenue.</p>
