<p data-index="1596"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="17-12" id="Page_17-12" data-index="1597"></span>The accounting and reporting for equity securities therefore depend on the level of influence and the type of security involved, as shown in <a class="blue" id="c17-fig-0013-1" href="#c17-fig-0013" data-index="1598" data-section-index="27" data-section-idref="c17-fig-0013" data-target-data-index="1600"><b data-index="1599">Illustration 17.13</b></a>.</p>
