<p data-index="3816">A market appraisal indicates that the time value of the option at March 31, 2020, is $100.<a href="#c17-note-0023-a" id="c17-note-0023" data-index="3817" data-section-index="27" data-section-idref="c17-note-0023-a" data-target-data-index="10892"><sup data-index="3818">23</sup></a> The company records this change in value of the option as follows.</p>
