<br data-index="5905">
<h3 data-index="5906"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="17-50" id="Page_17-50" data-index="5907"></span><span class="codeColorBlue3" data-index="5908">WileyPLUS</span></h3>
<aside data-index="5909">
<div class="top hr" data-index="5910"><hr data-index="5911"></div>
<section class="feature2" data-index="5912">
<p data-index="5913">Brief Exercises, Exercises, Problems, Problem Solution Walkthrough Videos, and many more learning and assessment tools and resources are available for practice in WileyPLUS.</p>
<div class="bottom hr" data-index="5914"><hr data-index="5915"></div>
</section>
</aside>
