<p id="c17-ex-0018" data-index="6323"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="6324"><b data-index="6325">E17.5</b></span> <b class="red" data-index="6326">(LO <a href="#lo_1" data-index="6327" data-section-index="27" data-section-idref="lo_1" data-target-data-index="83">1</a>)</b> <img style=" vertical-align: middle;" src="https://ereader-books-prod.chegg.com/682/9781119503682/39c53495-be04-40a4-af01-80a39a7df223/OPS/images/excel.jpg" alt="An icon reading text, “Excel”" data-index="6328" data-size="%7B%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D"> <b data-index="6329">(Effective-Interest versus Straight-Line Bond Amortization) </b>On January 1, 2020, Phantom Company acquires $200,000 of Spiderman Products, Inc., 9% bonds at a price of $185,589. Interest is received on January 1 of each year, and the bonds mature on January 1, 2023. The investment will provide Phantom Company a 12% yield. The bonds are classified as held-to-maturity.</p>
