<p data-index="6339"><b data-index="6340">&nbsp;c.</b><span class="Times" data-index="6341">&nbsp;Prepare the journal entry for the interest revenue and discount amortization under the straight-line method at Decem</span><span class="Times" data-index="6342">ber 31, 2021.</span></p>
<p data-index="6343"><b data-index="6344">&nbsp;d.</b><span class="Times" data-index="6345">&nbsp;Prepare the journal entry for the interest revenue and discount amortization under the effective-interest method at December 31, 2021.</span></p>
