<h5 data-index="7345"><span class="red" data-index="7346">Instructions</span></h5>
<p data-index="7347"><span class="Times" data-index="7348">Present the journal entries for the following dates/transactions.</span></p>
<p data-index="7349"><b data-index="7350">&nbsp;a.&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7351">May 1, 2020—Inception of futures contract, no premium paid.</span></p>
<p data-index="7352"><b data-index="7353">&nbsp;b.</b><b data-index="7354">&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7355">June 30, 2020—Hart prepares financial statements.</span></p>
<p data-index="7356"><b data-index="7357">&nbsp;c.&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7358">September 30, 2020—Hart prepares financial statements.</span></p>
<p data-index="7359"><b data-index="7360">&nbsp;d.&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7361">October 5, 2020—Hart purchases 200 ounces of titanium at $525 per ounce and settles the futures contract.</span></p>
<p data-index="7362"><b data-index="7363">&nbsp;e.&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7364">December 15, 2020—Hart sells clubs containing titanium purchased in October 2020 for $250,000. The cost of the finished goods inventory is $140,000.</span></p>
<p data-index="7365"><b data-index="7366">&nbsp;f.&nbsp;</b><span class="Times" data-index="7367">Indicate the amount(s) reported in the income statement related to the futures contract and the inventory transactions on December 31, 2020.</span></p>
