<p class="latin1" data-index="8169"><span class="label" data-index="8170"><b data-index="8171">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What should be reported on Fernandez's December 31, 2021, balance sheet? What should be reported on Fernandez's 2021 income statement?</p>
