<h4 data-index="8977"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="8978">Codification Exercises</span></h4>
<p data-index="8979">If your school has a subscription to the FASB Codification, log in and prepare responses to the following. Provide Codification references for your responses.</p>
<p id="c17-ex-0066" data-index="8980"><b data-index="8981"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="8982">CE17.1</span></b> Access the glossary (“Master Glossary”) to answer the following.</p>
<p data-index="8983"><b data-index="8984">&nbsp;a.</b>&nbsp;What are trading securities?</p>
<p data-index="8985"><b data-index="8986">&nbsp;b.</b>&nbsp;What is the definition of “holding gain or loss”?</p>
<p data-index="8987"><b data-index="8988">&nbsp;c.</b>&nbsp;What is a cash flow hedge?</p>
<p data-index="8989"><b data-index="8990">&nbsp;d.</b>&nbsp;What is a fair value hedge?</p>
