<p data-index="9878">On January 23, 2021, Republic sold all of its Burberry ordinary shares, receiving $287,220. <a class="blue" id="c17-fig-0056-1" href="#c17-fig-0056" data-index="9879" data-section-index="27" data-section-idref="c17-fig-0056" data-target-data-index="9881"><b data-index="9880">Illustration IFRS17.7</b></a> shows the computation of the realized gain on the sale.</p>
<figure id="c17-fig-0056" data-index="9881">
<table class="table" data-index="9882">
<colgroup data-index="9883"></colgroup>
