<h5 data-index="10573"><span class="red" data-index="10574">Instructions</span></h5>
<blockquote data-index="10575">
<p data-index="10576"><b data-index="10577">&nbsp;a.</b>&nbsp;Prepare the journal entry at the date of the bond purchase.</p>
<p data-index="10578"><b data-index="10579">&nbsp;b.</b>&nbsp;Prepare the journal entries to record the interest revenue and recognition of fair value for 2020.</p>
<p data-index="10580"><b data-index="10581">&nbsp;c.</b>&nbsp;Prepare the journal entry to record the recognition of fair value for 2021.</p>
</blockquote>
<p id="c17-ex-0083" data-index="10582"><b data-index="10583"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="10584">IFRS17.14</span></b> On December 21, 2020, Zurich Company provided you with the following information regarding its trading investments.</p>
